{"tid":1908283,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［推上熱門］簡短地描述點解泛民今次要進攻功能組別，想為香港好既入一入嚟。","createTime":"2020-03-03T07:18:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-03T07:47:01.000Z","uid":60916,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"643fcd402061abbdb529651e4f722954d9ab72e9","tid":1908283,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T07:18:15.000Z","msg":"如果功能組別是可以靠選舉爭取的，即代表泛民不必要地收了三十年捐款，有低成本爭取民主的方法而不用，連累無數人被囚甚至死亡。如果泛民沒有瞞騙選民，只是現在才想到這策略，即是泛民運作了三十年才研究功能組別的制度。<br />\n<br />\n如果功能組別是不可以靠選舉爭取的，即是泛民在愚弄選民做無用的事。<br />\n<br />\n結論：泛民一是瞞騙選民，一是尸位素餐三十年後一夜覺悟，一是愚弄選民，沒有其他可能性。"},{"pid":"c859cbba6c7349d79f49c31b8aa84a13c66c2aac","tid":1908283,"uid":63045,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T07:19:36.000Z","msg":"樓主係著名五毛山齊士<br />\n改咗名都認住你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2ff99e7fbb23e3fed8b069eba68e93f2d094767","tid":1908283,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c859cbba6c7349d79f49c31b8aa84a13c66c2aac","tid":1908283,"uid":63045,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T07:19:36.000Z","msg":"樓主係著名五毛山齊士<br />\n改咗名都認住你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T07:21:31.000Z","msg":"笑而不語"},{"pid":"674e3a602daeaaf9fcabe73b730f18d2ac9eb834","tid":1908283,"uid":221024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T07:23:08.000Z","msg":"【長文】立法會選舉部署！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1908281\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1908281</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a452b421ae34f7064bc8d712cf157c8548594981","tid":1908283,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T